title: Титаны
overview: Artificial intelligence challenges the strongest people in Russia. TNT TV channel is conducting an incredible sports experiment using the latest technologies. After analyzing a huge amount of data, the neural network has created a series of complex tests to test what the human body is capable of. In the special space of our experiment, the strongest people in Russia, real Titans, will compete for the title of the strongest winner of the show and a prize of 10 million rubles. Will people be able to withstand the power of artificial intelligence?
